    "softwareType": "IOS",
    "softwareVariant": "XE",
    "templateContent": "## Configuring Access Ports with Basic For-Each Loop ##\n\n## Define a list containing multiple ranges\n#set($InterfaceRangeList = [[$Range1Start..$Range1End],[$Range2Start..$Range2End],[$Range3Start..$Range3End]])\n\n## Iterate through each range, then through each integer in that range\n#foreach($range in $InterfaceRangeList)\n#foreach($access_port in $range)\ninterface GigabitEthernet1/0/$access_port\ndescription Access Port\nswitchport mode access\nswitchport access vlan 200\nswitchport voice vlan 20\nspanning-tree portfast\nspanning-tree bpduguard enable\nspanning-tree guard root\n\n#end\n#end\n\n\n",
